. Cult British TV Comedy will be of interest to both students and fans of modern TV comedy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCult filmszGreat Britain. 0aTelevision comedieszGreat Britain. 4aFilm and Media Studies 2021. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aBritish Television.  aCult TV.  aPost-alternative comedy.  aTV Comedy.1 aHunt, Leon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152610235540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526102355423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526102355/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles